<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She recently returned from a sun-soaked holiday to Crete with her co-star boyfriend Dan Edgar.</p>

<p>And Amber Turner was pining for her Greek getaway as she took to Instagram on Friday to post a stunning throwback snap.  </p>

